<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.5.4">
<l>peṟṟār taḷaikaḻalap pērntaṅ kayaliṭat</l>
<l>tuṟṟā roruvaru miṉṟi yulakiṉil,</l>
<l>maṟṟāru mañcappōy vañcappeṇ nañcuṇṭa</l>
<l>kaṟṟāya ṉēkoṭṭāy cappāṇi</l>
<l rend="indent">kārvaṇṇaṉē koṭṭāy cappāṇi.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Calf herder who, having returned so that his parents’ fetters loosened,</l>
<l>Having gone there to that place nearby without anyone who was a relation</l>
<l>So that his enemies in the world were terrified,</l>
<l>Ate the poison of a cruel woman, clap your hands;</l>
<l rend="indent">storm-hued one, clap your hands!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
